1b:["$","div",null,{"className":"routineFitCard","children":[["$","span",null,{"className":"eyebrow","children":"Fits these routines"}],[["$","div","beauty",{"children":[["$","strong",null,{"children":"Beauty, hair and skin"}],["$","p",null,{"children":"Collagen, biotin, and beauty-from-within support for skin, hair, and nails routines."}]]}],["$","div","family",{"children":[["$","strong",null,{"children":"Family gummies"}],["$","p",null,{"children":"Easy gummy formats for men, women, and children who prefer chewable supplements."}]]}]]]}]
1c:[["$","span",null,{"className":"eyebrow","children":"Product overview"}],["$","h2",null,{"children":"What Are WeightWorld’s Multivitamin Gummies for Women?"}],[["$","p","Did you know roughly 70% of women across the world are multivitamin deficient ? Are you sure you aren’t one of them? Although we get multivitamins from our foods, it’s important to understand that women have unique multivitamin requirements than men. So, you need a multivitamin supplement that specifically caters to women’s health needs . That’s why we introduce our Multivitamin Gummies for Women!",{"children":"Did you know roughly 70% of women across the world are multivitamin deficient ? Are you sure you aren’t one of them? Although we get multivitamins from our foods, it’s important to understand that women have unique multivitamin requirements than men. So, you need a multivitamin supplement that specifically caters to women’s health needs . That’s why we introduce our Multivitamin Gummies for Women!"}],["$","p","Unlike regular multivitamin supplements, our women’s Multivitamin Gummies pack all the vital vitamins, minerals, fatty acids and compounds that are recommended for optimising female wellness. Here’s the best part! Our easy-to-chew gummies come in a fruity Strawberry & Raspberry flavour , making your multivitamin dose a daily treat, not a chore! So, don’t settle for less when you can thrive with our Multivitamin Gummies for Women!",{"children":"Unlike regular multivitamin supplements, our women’s Multivitamin Gummies pack all the vital vitamins, minerals, fatty acids and compounds that are recommended for optimising female wellness. Here’s the best part! Our easy-to-chew gummies come in a fruity Strawberry & Raspberry flavour , making your multivitamin dose a daily treat, not a chore! So, don’t settle for less when you can thrive with our Multivitamin Gummies for Women!"}]]]
1d:["$","div",null,{"className":"productAccordions","children":[[["$","details","How Our Multivitamin Gummies Benefit Women?",{"className":"productAccordion","open":true,"children":[["$","summary",null,{"children":"How Our Multivitamin Gummies Benefit Women?"}],["$","div",null,{"className":"accordionBody","children":[[["$","p","While we already know multivitamins are important for our bodies, let’s find out how the powerful nutrients in our Multivitamin Gummies help you tick your well-being and beauty goals!",{"children":"While we already know multivitamins are important for our bodies, let’s find out how the powerful nutrients in our Multivitamin Gummies help you tick your well-being and beauty goals!"}],["$","p","Women’s monthly cycles are regulated by the release of hormones. Iodine contributes to the normal production of thyroid hormones and Vitamin B6 contributes to the regulation of hormonal activity. Plus, Evening Primrose is known to support women’s cycles and help manage the PMS struggles.",{"children":"Women’s monthly cycles are regulated by the release of hormones. Iodine contributes to the normal production of thyroid hormones and Vitamin B6 contributes to the regulation of hormonal activity. Plus, Evening Primrose is known to support women’s cycles and help manage the PMS struggles."}],["$","p","Vitamins A, B7, C, Iodine and Zinc support youthful skin while Biotin (B7) and Zinc help in the maintenance of your hair. Evening Primrose Oil and Hyaluronic Acid (HLA) are also perfect for managing the appearance of ageing and maintaining gorgeous hair, helping you rediscover your natural beauty.",{"children":"Vitamins A, B7, C, Iodine and Zinc support youthful skin while Biotin (B7) and Zinc help in the maintenance of your hair. Evening Primrose Oil and Hyaluronic Acid (HLA) are also perfect for managing the appearance of ageing and maintaining gorgeous hair, helping you rediscover your natural beauty."}],["$","p","Calcium, Iodine and vitamins B6, B7, B12 & C contribute to normal energy-yielding metabolism, which is ideal for food regulation and replenishing your energy. Coenzyme Q10 also assists in the production of natural ATP energy levels, helping you re-energise after a hectic day.",{"children":"Calcium, Iodine and vitamins B6, B7, B12 & C contribute to normal energy-yielding metabolism, which is ideal for food regulation and replenishing your energy. Coenzyme Q10 also assists in the production of natural ATP energy levels, helping you re-energise after a hectic day."}],["$","p","Calcium, Zinc, Vitamin C, Evening Primrose Oil and HLA support your bone strength. Besides bone strength, Calcium and HLA are known to be ideal for joint flexibility, assisting you in easy mobility.",{"children":"Calcium, Zinc, Vitamin C, Evening Primrose Oil and HLA support your bone strength. Besides bone strength, Calcium and HLA are known to be ideal for joint flexibility, assisting you in easy mobility."}],["$","p","Vitamins A, B6, B9, B12, C and E, Zinc and Coenzyme Q10 are credited for helping fortify your bodily resistance against unwanted invaders in your bodies.",{"children":"Vitamins A, B6, B9, B12, C and E, Zinc and Coenzyme Q10 are credited for helping fortify your bodily resistance against unwanted invaders in your bodies."}]],["$","ul",null,{"children":[["$","li","Women’s Cycle",{"children":"Women’s Cycle"}],["$","li","Skin & Hair",{"children":"Skin & Hair"}],"$L1e","$L1f","$L20"]}]]}]]}],"$L21"],"$L22","$L23","$L24","$L25"]}]
