21:["$","details","Why Choose Our Multivitamin Gummies for Women?",{"className":"productAccordion","open":false,"children":[["$","summary",null,{"children":"Why Choose Our Multivitamin Gummies for Women?"}],["$","div",null,{"className":"accordionBody","children":[[["$","p","Our Strawberry- and Raspberry-flavoured gummies offer you a tasty and easy-to-chew way to get all the essential nutrients, unlike bitter and hard-to-swallow multivitamin tablets",{"children":"Our Strawberry- and Raspberry-flavoured gummies offer you a tasty and easy-to-chew way to get all the essential nutrients, unlike bitter and hard-to-swallow multivitamin tablets"}],["$","p","Although our gummies have a sweet fruity taste to tantalise your taste buds, their low sugar content takes away all the negatives of a sweet treat.",{"children":"Although our gummies have a sweet fruity taste to tantalise your taste buds, their low sugar content takes away all the negatives of a sweet treat."}],["$","p","Unlike chemical-laden tablets, our gummies are all-natural and free from GMOs, gluten and artificial additives, making sure you face no known harmful side effects while enjoying the benefits",{"children":"Unlike chemical-laden tablets, our gummies are all-natural and free from GMOs, gluten and artificial additives, making sure you face no known harmful side effects while enjoying the benefits"}]],["$","ul",null,{"children":[["$","li","While there are many multivitamin supplements available on the market, here’s what makes our Multivitamin Gummies for Women stand out from the rest!",{"children":"While there are many multivitamin supplements available on the market, here’s what makes our Multivitamin Gummies for Women stand out from the rest!"}],["$","li","Advanced Formula",{"children":"Advanced Formula"}],["$","li","Power-packed with 10 vitamins and minerals plus HLA, Coenzyme Q10 and omega-rich Evening Primrose Oil, a revolutionary formula hard to find elsewhere",{"children":"Power-packed with 10 vitamins and minerals plus HLA, Coenzyme Q10 and omega-rich Evening Primrose Oil, a revolutionary formula hard to find elsewhere"}],["$","li","Tablets? Nay! Gummies? Yay!",{"children":"Tablets? Nay! Gummies? Yay!"}],["$","li","Low in Sugar, Not Sweetness",{"children":"Low in Sugar, Not Sweetness"}],["$","li","Say No To Side Effects",{"children":"Say No To Side Effects"}],["$","li","Enjoy Higher Supply Than Others",{"children":"Enjoy Higher Supply Than Others"}],["$","li","With 90 gummies per pack, you get an uninterrupted 1.5 months’ supply, higher than what other multivitamin gummy supplements offer",{"children":"With 90 gummies per pack, you get an uninterrupted 1.5 months’ supply, higher than what other multivitamin gummy supplements offer"}],["$","li","100% Satisfaction Guarantee",{"children":"100% Satisfaction Guarantee"}],["$","li","We offer you a 90-day full money-back guarantee so you can try our gummies risk-free!",{"children":"We offer you a 90-day full money-back guarantee so you can try our gummies risk-free!"}]]}]]}]]}]
